      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_street-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん、新しい服がほしいって言ってたでしょ？\nここで見ていったらどうかな",
      "startTime": 5.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "って、あれ……？\nお、お姉ちゃん、なんで泣いてるの？",
      "startTime": 9.8194502667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "だって千紗が、私のために編集部の人達に連絡して……\nスタンプラリーまで、手作りしてくれて……",
      "startTime": 18.0000002861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "一生懸命、頑張ってくれたんだって思うと\nそれだけで……",
      "startTime": 23.9666669528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、千紗。何かほしいものはない？\nお姉ちゃんが買ってあげる。新しい服がいいかしら",
      "startTime": 29.0000002861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "お、お姉ちゃん落ち着いて。お誕生日なんだから\nお姉ちゃんがほしいものを買わなきゃ",
      "startTime": 37.5333336194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　あそこのお店なんてどうかな。お姉ちゃん\n綺麗だし、ああいう大人っぽい服も似合いそう",
      "startTime": 44.9159200034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうかしら\nふふ、綺麗だなんて、もぉ……",
      "startTime": 51.6877154746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "……あら？　その隣の服って……\nとっても可愛いわね。ちょっと試着してみようかしら",
      "startTime": 60.9653515654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "千紗、少し待っててくれる？",
      "startTime": 65.3396190806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "ふぇ？　お姉ちゃん？",
      "startTime": 67.9115463498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせ\nふふ、気に入ったからそのまま買ってきちゃった",
      "startTime": 74.3333376885,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "どうかしら、せっかくのお誕生日企画だし\n少しだけ気合いを入れてみたんだけど",
      "startTime": 81.7000053724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "え……",
      "startTime": 84.4361308259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん！　髪型、とっても可愛いと思う！\n服は……お、同じようなの、持ってた気もするけど……",
      "startTime": 91.4666720391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ありがとう、千紗\n最近お仕事が忙しくて、買いに来る時間がなかったの",
      "startTime": 99.0000068983,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、そろそろ次の場所に行きましょうか\n次は、『遊園地』ね",
      "startTime": 107.766673565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～、普段は繋がりのない場所が繋がっていく\nやっぱりスタンプラリーはいいわね、わくわくしちゃう",
      "startTime": 115.8102054895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あはは……お洋服、私が選んであげた方が良かった\nのかなぁ……。嬉しそうだし、いいんだけど……",
      "startTime": 125.8000068983,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_photo_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "一個目のスタンプの形、アルファベットの『H』に\n見えるわね。二箇所目は『O』……何かの暗号かしら",
      "startTime": 136.1000068983,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、スタンプラリー、楽しんでくれてるみたい",
      "startTime": 145.2217972519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん、それは最後のお楽しみだよ\nそれよりほら、遊園地に着いたよ！",
      "startTime": 153.7348016186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……二人で来るのはいつぶりかしら\nあのメリーゴーラウンド、昔一緒に乗ったわよね",
      "startTime": 161.7333432835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　そういえばここって、水族館もあったわね\n千紗ってば、くらげの水槽にずーっと張り付いてたのよ",
      "startTime": 170.0333483697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、ふわふわしてて綺麗だから、かな？\nお姉ちゃんは、よくペンギンさんを見てなかった？",
      "startTime": 179.4000150364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、よちよち歩いているのに、水に入ったら凄い\nスピードで泳ぎだして。びっくりしたのを覚えてるわ",
      "startTime": 188.219249908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "不思議だったから\n帰った後、急いで図鑑で調べたっけ",
      "startTime": 194.0000150364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "くらげのことも調べてくれたよね\nあ、でもね、今日は別の建物に入ろうと思ってるの",
      "startTime": 199.7000089329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski017.m4a",
